author: jta
msg: DERBY-1986 Generalizing the bis_DERBY.rdf file to reduce release maintenance.
The initial version I checked in requires the file to be updated with each
new release (and the http://www.apache.org/licenses/exports/ must be rebuilt).
Since the id of source distributions at archive.apache.org/dist/db/derby/
is pretty obvious, we can point to that higher level directory like James does.
Also Derby does not include nor ship the JCE (if Derby did ship/include and if
the bits comprising the JCE were to change, new entries would be needed).
